---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const site='https://jacksonlotstriping.com';
const schemas=[{'@context':'https://schema.org','@type':'BreadcrumbList','itemListElement':[{'@type':'ListItem','position':1,'name':'Home','item':site+'/'},{'@type':'ListItem','position':2,'name':'Contact','item':site+'/contact/'}]}];
---
<BaseLayout title="Contact Jackson Lot Striping | Request a Quote" description="Request a Jackson MS parking lot striping quote, site visit, ADA evaluation, overnight striping estimate, or lot photo review." canonical={site + '/contact/'} schemas={schemas}>
  <section class="page-hero"><div class="container"><p class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a> / Contact</p><h1>Contact Jackson Lot Striping</h1><p>Send the address, photos, and timing notes. We will review the lot, ask any needed follow-up questions, and let you know whether a site visit is needed.</p></div></section>
  <section class="section"><div class="container split"><article><h2>Get a Practical Estimate</h2><p><strong>Address:</strong> Jackson, MS</p><p>The fastest estimates include the property address, approximate number of spaces, service needed, current photos, and whether the lot can be closed during the day, after hours, overnight, or in phases.</p><p>Weather can affect scheduling. Rain, wet pavement, fresh sealcoat, heat, and humidity may move the job window so the markings have a better chance to cure cleanly.</p><h2>Common Requests</h2><ul class="check-list"><li>Request Site Visit</li><li>Upload Parking Lot Photos</li><li>Request ADA Evaluation</li><li>Get Overnight Striping Quote</li></ul></article><article class="quote-card"><h2>Request Quote</h2><form id="quote-form" class="form-grid" name="quote" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data" action="https://api.web3forms.com/submit"><input type="hidden" name="access_key" value="cc5a272b-2fea-464a-8999-adec3dbddef4" /><input type="hidden" name="subject" value="Jackson Lot Striping contact form" /><label>Name<input name="name" autocomplete="name" required /></label><label>Company<input name="company" autocomplete="organization" /></label><label>Phone<input name="phone" type="tel" autocomplete="tel" required /></label><label>Email<input name="email" type="email" autocomplete="email" /></label><label>Property Address<input name="property-address" autocomplete="street-address" required /></label><label>Service Needed<select name="service"><option>Request Site Visit</option><option>Upload Parking Lot Photos</option><option>Request ADA Evaluation</option><option>Get Overnight Striping Quote</option><option>Parking Lot Re-Striping</option><option>Fire Lane Painting</option><option>Thermoplastic Question</option><option>Layout Planning</option></select></label><label>Preferred Schedule<select name="preferred-schedule"><option>Normal business hours are okay</option><option>After hours</option><option>Overnight</option><option>Weekend</option><option>Phased by section</option><option>Not sure yet</option></select></label><label>Approximate Number of Spaces<input name="approximate-spaces" inputmode="numeric" /></label><label>Upload Parking Lot Photos <span class="field-note">Photos help us estimate faded markings, ADA areas, fire lanes, and pavement condition.</span><input name="attachment" type="file" accept="image/*,.pdf" multiple /></label><label>Project Details<textarea name="message" rows="5" placeholder="Tell us about faded lines, sealcoating timing, ADA concerns, tenant access, weather-sensitive scheduling, or overnight needs."></textarea></label><button class="button" type="submit">Send Quote Request</button></form></article></div></section>
</BaseLayout>
